'''Domain Shen'g''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

During the [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Defense of Mon Calamari]], the vessels of Domain Shen'g were redirected to [[Contruum/Legends|Contruum]] to eventually reinforce [[Coruscant/Legends|Yuuzhan'tar]].<ref name="TUF" />

